dialog.body: Welcome to Old Stone Auto Insurance. My name is Noah Peterson. May I please have your name?
Hello, my name is Mary Harris.
Nice to meet you, Mary. Could you kindly provide me with your date of birth?
Sure, my date of birth is February fifth, nineteen ninety-eight.
Thank you, Mary. Can you also confirm your residential address for our records?
Of course, my address is one two three Main Street, Anytown, ABC123.
Great, thank you for confirming your details, Mary. Is there anything specific you would like to discuss or inquire about today?
I was hoping to check the status of my recent claim on my policy.
I can assist you with that, Mary. Thank you for providing the details. Let me look that up for you. Please hold on for a moment.
Thank you for your patience, Mary. I have checked your claim status. I will provide you with an update shortly. Thank you for reaching out to Old Stone Auto Insurance.
